because...

386
00:14:16,251 --> 00:14:18,797
I thought tonight
would be the night when...

387
00:14:19,366 --> 00:14:21,252
When I told you something.

388
00:14:21,463 --> 00:14:23,466
Reggie, I've been
waiting for this.

389
00:14:23,486 --> 00:14:25,850
- You have?
- Yeah.

390
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:28,295
Well, I mean, I didn't know that
aliens could swing that way,

391
00:14:28,315 --> 00:14:30,622
