with Jeremy the jock...

397
00:14:42,233 --> 00:14:44,517
And that I'm your soul mate.

398
00:14:45,559 --> 00:14:46,854
Oh.

399
00:14:48,616 --> 00:14:50,929
Reggie,
I think you're great,

400
00:14:50,949 --> 00:14:54,226
but until tonight,
you were my only friend.

401
00:14:55,640 --> 00:14:58,348
And you're probably still
my only real friend.

402
00:14:59,043 --> 00:15:01,706
I just don't know if I really
see you that other way.

403
00:15:05,707 --> 00:15:06,912
I'm sorry.

404
00:15:10,263 --> 00:15:12,757
This is the worst thing
I've ever felt!

405
00:15:12,918 --> 00:15:15,938
