because she has learned

431
00:16:05,196 --> 00:16:07,881
it isn't Marty, but she
will get back out there,

432
00:16:07,901 --> 00:16:10,556
and she will find him,
despite her age.

433
00:16:10,576 --> 00:16:13,286
No. No.
That's not it at all.

434
00:16:13,306 --> 00:16:15,706
I mean, Marty may have been
a completely revolting

435
00:16:15,726 --> 00:16:17,133
little monster
of a 16-year-old,

436
00:16:17,153 --> 00:16:19,528
but he made me laugh
that night instead of cry.

437
00:16:19,548 --> 00:16:21,188
And there have been
a million times since

438
00:16:21,208 --> 00:16:23,450
where he has turned
my tears into laughter,

439
00:16:23,484 --> 00:16:25,891
often via
the Weaver running man...

440
00:16:25,911 --> 00:16:27,987
