and move on.

445
00:16:42,045 --> 00:16:45,681
There are drummers
in your future. Trust me.

446
00:16:47,295 --> 00:16:49,620
Wow. She knows a lot.

447
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:51,514
Yes, she does.

448
00:16:51,700 --> 00:16:54,111
I think I'm gonna
go back to the dance.

449
00:16:54,131 --> 00:16:55,769
Go, my son.

450
00:16:55,906 --> 00:16:58,003
